data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This magnificent two-story features 5 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms, offering the perfect blend of space, style, and comfort. The floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an inviting atmosphere for both daily living and entertaining. The kitchen boasts modern appliances and ample counter space. In addition, the large, main floor office offers ideal working space. Upstairs, discover 4 spacious bedrooms, with the master suite being a true retreat, complete with a luxurious en-suite bathroom and walk-in closet. The additional bedrooms are versatile and perfect for accommodating family or guests. Step outside to the well-manicured backyard, perfect for outdoor gatherings and enjoying the fresh air. With thoughtful landscaping and a serene ambiance, the outdoor space is an extension of the home's charm. Welcome to your dream home! Association fees include snow cleaning of private road and landscaping/maintenance of common areas.
